    <item>
      <title>亚当斯让马姆达尼在伊丽莎白街花园上建造变得更加困难</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2025/11/12/nyregion/elizabeth-street-garden-parkland.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市长埃里克·亚当斯 (Eric Adams) 的政府正在将这座花园指定为公园用地，这可能会阻碍当选市长佐赫兰·马姆达尼 (Zohran Mamdani) 誓言重振在那里修建经济适用房的斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2025/11/12/nyregion/elizabeth-street-garden-parkland.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Nov 2025 22:41:24 GMT</pubDate>
